5. LEGO: LEGO is a company that produces a wide range of collectible toy building sets and minifigures. Many of their collectibles are highly sought after by collectors and can be worth a significant amount of money, particularly if they are rare or hard to find.
6. Hot Wheels: Hot Wheels is a company that produces a wide range of collectible toy cars and playsets. Many of their collectibles are highly sought after by collectors and can be worth a significant amount of money, particularly if they are rare or hard to find.
